  ('b348eaf8-b027-4913-908f-aee4e7475782', 'a0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001', 'Tiffany''s The Club', 'tiffanys-the-club', 'Madrid', 'Other', 'Tiffany’s The Club Madrid is a long-standing and well-known nightlife destination located in the Doctor Arce. The venue is recognized for its energetic and accessible atmosphere, attracting a young and diverse crowd, including both locals and international visitors. With its classic club layout, spacious dance floor, and vibrant lighting, Tiffany’s delivers a straightforward, high-energy party experience focused on music and social interaction.

The club has built its reputation on consistency and lively nights, making it a reliable choice for those looking for a fun and dynamic environment without the ultra-exclusive barriers of some upscale venues. Its central location and strong student appeal contribute to its popularity within Madrid’s nightlife scene.', 'https://ovyfdjqltpqqkffjpnfe.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/clubs/1778083497796-684234552178780138535776364068457870269979437n.jpg', ARRAY['https://ovyfdjqltpqqkffjpnfe.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/clubs/1778083502905-683365153178780138685776363430857771650360384n.jpg', 'https://ovyfdjqltpqqkffjpnfe.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/clubs/1778083509450-683766532178780138295776364606196025106905310n.jpg', 'https://ovyfdjqltpqqkffjpnfe.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/clubs/1778083507883-683879423180817569592682628961454964168917910n.jpg', 'https://ovyfdjqltpqqkffjpnfe.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/clubs/1778083505299-682644670180817568752682624698018229850742840n.jpg'], 'tiffanystheclub', 'https://reservas.tiffanystheclub.com/en/', ARRAY[]::text[], 18, 'Smart Casual', 'Avenida Doctor Arce 10, Madrid, Spain 28002', 40.4474957, -3.6805514, true, 18),
